<h2>Bruising or discoloration, Coated or furry tongue and White patches on tongue</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms bruising or discoloration, coated or furry tongue and white patches on tongue including Bruise or contusion, Hematoma, and Trauma or injury.</p>
